(44, 27, 1, 19, 33, 11, 11, 'delivered Paul and certain other prisoners', 'Divine Guidance in Adversity', 'This connection highlights the theme of God''s enduring counsel amidst human circumstances. Paul''s journey to Italy under Roman authority reflects the idea that the Lord''s thoughts guide events across generations.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
